<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>ì˜¤ë½ì‹¤ ìŠˆíŒ… ê²Œì„</title>
<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    background: black;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}
canvas {
    background: #111;
    display: block;
    margin: 20px auto;
    cursor: crosshair;
}
#info {
    font-size: 18px;
}
#reload {
    color: orange;
    font-weight: bold;
}
</style>
